but I was serious about building
that nice house with a big yard.

7
00:00:33,563 --> 00:00:35,723
It would be on a hill where
we could see the ocean,

8
00:00:35,803 --> 00:00:38,563
complete with a state-of-the-art
system kitchen and basement studio.

9
00:00:40,003 --> 00:00:42,443
In your closet would be

10
00:00:42,503 --> 00:00:45,003
a whole line of clothes
of the latest fashion,

11
00:00:46,113 --> 00:00:50,343
so that you'd have a smile on
your face every time you came home,

12
00:00:50,413 --> 00:00:53,013
even with your tendency to
have your heart broken by men.

13
00:01:05,463 --> 00:01:09,773
Blinking eyes call the wind

14
00:01:09,773 --> 00:01:17,413
A smile clears all the noise away

15
00:01:17,413 --> 00:01:23,973
The angel in your eyes whispers

16
00:01:24,213 --> 00:01:29,153
"Everything begins now"

17
