Can you feel it now
Can you feel it now

18
00:01:31,393 --> 00:01:35,193
It's like being caught in a wave

19
00:01:35,193 --> 00:01:37,363
Pulling on my heart
Pulling on my heart

20
00:01:37,363 --> 00:01:40,833
Breath held, arms reaching out

21
00:01:40,833 --> 00:01:48,073
Baby this world is
different from yesterday's

22
00:01:48,303 --> 00:01:52,713
You're the only one I can see

23
00:01:52,713 --> 00:01:56,643
Baby my wish on a wing

24
00:01:56,883 --> 00:01:59,623
This sky is torn

25
00:01:59,623 --> 00:02:05,023
By a single overflowing word

26
00:02:40,593 --> 00:02:41,893
One way ticket to Tokyo.

27
00:02:42,493 --> 00:02:44,223
The trains are running late
because of the snow.

28
00:02:44,463 --> 00:02:45,623
Anything will do
as long as it gets me there.

29
00:03:08,683 --> 00:03:10,353
You didn't hafta
come see me off.

30
00:03:14,863 --> 00:03:18,093
I called in sick and took the day off
to come see you off,

31
00:03:18,163 --> 00:03:19,593
so you could be nicer.

32
00:03:21,363 --> 00:03:23,493
You come alone?
What about Nobu?

33
00:03:24,433 --> 00:03:26,233
He's probably home crying
about now.

34
00:03:26,943 --> 00:03:29,103
After all, you only told him yesterday.

35
00:03:29,843 --> 00:03:32,203
Put yourself in the position
of those who are left behind.

36
00:03:33,343 --> 00:03:36,743
Sorry. I struggled to find
the right time to tell you guys.

37
00:03:38,183 --> 00:03:42,383
Although we knew that this day
would come eventually.

38
00:03:45,193 --> 00:03:45,953
What is it?

39
00:03:46,463 --> 00:03:47,623
Your birthday present.

40
00:03:47,993 --> 00:03:49,583
This piece of paper?

41
00:03:54,633 --> 00:03:56,003
REN

42
00:03:57,603 --> 00:04:01,543
Don't get me wrong!
I'm not going to Tokyo to see him!

43
00:04:01,873 --> 00:04:05,473
I know. That has nothing to do
with this.

44
00:04:07,883 --> 00:04:09,103
You don't understand.

45
00:04:10,683 --> 00:04:12,653
You don't understand anything.

46
